### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@productId = a1234567-89ab-4789-0123-456789abcdef

### Get all products with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?PageNumber=1&PageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Search Products - REGULAR Search (Default)
# Regular text search with keywords
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/search?SearchTerm=Apple Watch&Keywords=Laptop&Keywords=Monitor
    &SearchType=Regular&PageNumber=1&PageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Search Products - SEMANTIC Search
# Semantic search understanding meaning and context
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/search?SearchTerm=Apple Watch&SearchType=Semantic&PageNumber=1&PageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Search Products - HYBRID Search
# Combines regular and semantic search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/search?SearchTerm=Apple Watch&Keywords=Laptop&Keywords=Monitor&SearchType=Hybrid&PageNumber=1&PageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Get product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Accept: application/json

### Create a new product
# @name createProduct
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name": "MacBook Air M2 (13.6\")",
  "Description": "Slim aluminum design, M2 chip, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD, and all-day battery life.",
  "Price": 1499.00,
  "IsAvailable": true,
  "ImageUrl": "https://example.com/images/macbook-air-m2.jpg"
}

### Update a product (requires valid productId)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Id": "a1234567-89ab-4789-0123-456789abcdef",
  "Name": "Razer DeathAdder V3 Mouse",
  "Description": "30K DPI optical sensor, 9 programmable buttons, and ergonomic right-handed design.",
  "Price": 79.99,
  "IsAvailable": true,
  "ImageUrl": "https://example.com/images/razer-mouse.jpg"
}

### Delete a product (requires valid productId)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}